For \ourmethod, we use projections with {{2110.13883_FO0383||FO}} number of dimensions, {{2110.13883_FO0384||FO}} trees, and {{2110.13883_FO0385||FO}} minimum number of points in a node to consider it for splitting. These parameters are suggested by the authors of geodesic forests [madhyastha:20:gf].